      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Section 1444 describes renunciation of a betrothal agreement due to gross misconduct and related compensations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 1444 outlines the prescription period for claims for compensation related to renunciation of a betrothal agreement."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-32f0865d6629c46fe99f13ae20d441f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3a1cd577a93157d9b1c759e9c604a8c</data>
