    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SECTION 277 BIS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Section 277 bis specifies increased penalties for offences causing grievous bodily harm or death, with punishments ranging from fifteen to twenty years imprisonment to the death penalty."</data>
