      <data key="d1">"Section 272 covers the use of another's trade identity in various forms to mislead the public and gain unfair trade advantage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 272, though not fully detailed in the excerpt, is referenced concerning goods bearing forged or imitated trademarks, possibly outlining the specific criteria or definitions."</data>
