      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"An amendment to the criminal code executed in the year 2525 according to the Thai Buddhist Era calendaring system, which facilitated changes in Section 315 concerning intermediaries accepting property from offenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"This Act amended Section 276 of the Criminal Code, changing the legal parameters and penalties for certain offences."&lt;SEP&gt;"This is a legal amendment to the Criminal Code, specifically addressing changes to the penalties associated with robbery, reflecting legal developments in Thailand."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-b879f636061e8c548d80b7bcc128b902&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf2e9ba1c433d67ab7eef97426e05cd4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d23931e05623c30bf7072dff6eb48dd5</data>
