      <data key="d1">"Order (No. 41) is a legal amendment issued by the National Administrative Reform Council affecting various legal sections."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-526a0b152c10330561e4c72c14e89416</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CONCURRENCE OF OFFENCES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Concurrence of Offences refers to a situation where a single act violates multiple legal provisions and how it is punished."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-bd062f5650ed30bf931f3a519e8693ce</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DECREE (NO. 11)&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Decree (No. 11) is a legislative order given by the National Executive Council which included amendments to laws."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-526a0b152c10330561e4c72c14e89416</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;RECIDIVE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
