      <data key="d2">chunk-bd062f5650ed30bf931f3a519e8693ce</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BOOK 1 OF THIS CODE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Book 1 of this Code refers to a section within the legal code that is applicable to offenses according to other laws, provided no contrary legal prescriptions exist."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e8a12bcf29dd0e194c7a3e4a71523199</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;INQUIRY OFFICIAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"An Inquiry Official is an authorized personnel involved in legal investigations and conducting inquiries as part of the judicial process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Inquiry Official is responsible for investigating criminal cases and gathering information on offenses."&lt;SEP&gt;"Inquiry Officials are individuals with the power to investigate criminal cases."</data>
