      <data key="d1">"Section 267 outlines penalties for making false entries into public or official documents."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-0821966abff87f794597de47538cc67e</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SECTION 192&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Section 192 prescribes penalties for harboring or assisting escapees from lawful custody, aimed at preventing their re-arrest."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-268065f480c7c2e17bd0004a31f0f454</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OFFENCES RELATING TO DOCUMENTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Outlined in Sections 264 to 269, these offences involve the forgery, alteration, or misrepresentation of documents."&lt;SEP&gt;"These offences involve illegal activities related to the handling and falsification of documents, as specified in certain sections of the criminal code."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-a3d4a61fa1cf40d9a40ee60bcdbb217e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78de612c5be2681a856b09899b977bd3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FORFEITURE OF PROPERTY&quot;">
