      <data key="d2">chunk-e8a12bcf29dd0e194c7a3e4a71523199</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;OFFICIAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"An Official is a person in a position of authority who enforces laws and regulations, often requesting cooperation from the public."&lt;SEP&gt;"An official is a person holding a position of authority or service in an organization or government, responsible for various duties including managing activities, collecting taxes, and keeping records."&lt;SEP&gt;"An official refers to a person holding a public office, potentially involved in legal proceedings related to fines and orders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Official refers to individuals in various governmental roles with specific duties, such as making or receiving documents and executing laws."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e1e198b1f8b66564b0fae2fbe893a4c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee7dd29b88d53ea4523197532d9851fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a03e095c966911fdfbf17177a6fd05e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de71dcf326342843893937651bd927f6</data>
    </node>
