    <node id="&quot;OFFENDER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"An offender is a person who has been judged by the Court to have committed a crime and is subject to punishment and other legal actions."&lt;SEP&gt;"An offender is an individual who has committed a crime and may be subject to fines or other punishments."&lt;SEP&gt;"Offender is an individual who has committed an offense and may be subject to punishment according to legal guidelines."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Offender is an individual subject to punishment or rehabilitation conditions determined by the Court for committing an offence."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-7770756870427eb344039070455f889c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee7dd29b88d53ea4523197532d9851fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce00bf86a210ec770e6555803254e48b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e4efb3313af866dc7bcaba7c4daff62</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;AFFRAY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
