    <node id="&quot;IMPRISONMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Imprisonment is a form of punishment involving confinement for a period, which can be life-long and is subject to various legal stipulations and calculations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Imprisonment is a form of punishment mentioned multiple times, with varying durations based on the offense."&lt;SEP&gt;"Imprisonment is a legal punishment involving confinement in prison for various durations as outlined for different offences."&lt;SEP&gt;"Imprisonment is a legal punishment involving the confinement of a person, which is mentioned in the context of various offenses related to electronic card forgery."&lt;SEP&gt;"Imprisonment is a type of punishment wherein the offender is confined to a correctional facility for a certain period as determined by the Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"Imprisonment refers to the legal penalty involving incarceration for various crimes such as counterfeiting, as described in the text."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8898310f532e327f554bd8980c0ecbb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c70ada6cc5febef9164203734d211889&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-526a0b152c10330561e4c72c14e89416&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a12bcf29dd0e194c7a3e4a71523199&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78127285a70d48835c00c4ab2953f9f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-226c50ebda82206e6ae01871ad28a3a3</data>
    </node>
