    <node id="&quot;FINE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A Fine is a monetary penalty imposed as a punishment within the legal system."&lt;SEP&gt;"A Fine is a monetary penalty imposed by the Court on an offender as an alternative or addition to imprisonment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fine denotes a monetary penalty imposed as punishment for committing offences."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fine refers to a monetary penalty imposed on individuals as a punishment for offenses related to electronic card forgery and other trade offenses."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fine refers to the monetary penalty imposed along with or instead of imprisonment for various offenses."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8898310f532e327f554bd8980c0ecbb2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-526a0b152c10330561e4c72c14e89416&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8a12bcf29dd0e194c7a3e4a71523199&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78127285a70d48835c00c4ab2953f9f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-226c50ebda82206e6ae01871ad28a3a3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SECTION 30/1 AND SECTION 30/2&quot;">
