      <data key="d1">"Refers to the leading city and administrative center of Portugal, correctly identified as Lisbon."&lt;SEP&gt;"The term 'capital of Portugal' refers to the city serving as the political and administrative core, recognized as Lisbon."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-6e459e292c09831cb5355afa423a1cad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8527717aaf5c016fde3403d174020e30</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;CAPITAL OF ITALY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Refers to the leading city and administrative center of Italy, correctly identified as Rome."&lt;SEP&gt;"The term 'capital of Italy' refers to the city that serves as the administrative heart, known as Rome."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-6e459e292c09831cb5355afa423a1cad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8527717aaf5c016fde3403d174020e30</data>
