      <data key="d4">"The Minister of Interior handles appeals related to the registration of associations, making final decisions on these appeals."</data>
      <data key="d5">"appeal, decision-making"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-91e6c9c6ece02f3027772a9577efdcd4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ASSOCIATION&quot;" target="&quot;GOVERNMENT GAZETTE&quot;">
      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Once an association is registered, it is published in the Government Gazette, formally recognizing its legal status."</data>
      <data key="d5">"formal recognition, public notice"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-91e6c9c6ece02f3027772a9577efdcd4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ASSOCIATION&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 78&quot;">
      <data key="d3">7.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Section 78 outlines the basic requirements and framework for creating and registering an association."</data>
      <data key="d5">"regulation, foundational requirements"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-91e6c9c6ece02f3027772a9577efdcd4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ASSOCIATION&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 79&quot;">
      <data key="d3">8.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Section 79 provides the specific regulations required for an association, forming a guideline for correct registration."</data>
      <data key="d5">"regulatory compliance, guidelines"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-91e6c9c6ece02f3027772a9577efdcd4</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ASSOCIATION&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 84&quot;">
      <data key="d3">7.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Section 84 provides the procedure for formally modifying an association's regulations, ensuring changes are properly documented and legal."</data>
      <data key="d5">"regulatory update, legal procedure"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-91e6c9c6ece02f3027772a9577efdcd4</data>
    </edge>
