    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;SIN SUAN TUA&quot;" target="&quot;SIN SOMROS&quot;">
      <data key="d3">16.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"Sin Somros and Sin Suan Tua are two types of property categories in a marriage, with different rules regarding their use for debts and division upon marriage changes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Sin Suan Tua and Sin Somros are legal property categories that determine rights and management responsibilities between spouses."</data>
      <data key="d5">"property division, debt obligation"&lt;SEP&gt;"property rights, marital law"</data>
