      <data key="d3">17.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Court is involved in managing disputes and granting permissions related to the Sin Somros."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Court oversees decisions related to the management and division of Sin Somros in cases of spousal competence and custodian appointments."</data>
