    <edge source="&quot;LETTER&quot;" target="&quot;HIRER&quot;">
      <data key="d3">18.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Hirer enters into an agreement with the Letter, taking possession of the property and being subject to the contract's terms, while the Letter is responsible for providing a well-maintained property."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Letter leases out Property to the Hirer, and the Hirer is responsible for paying Rent."</data>
      <data key="d5">"lease agreement, payment"&lt;SEP&gt;"legal agreement, responsibilities"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-47c412635e02e67c8c5e723ae7e9d0ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd6efc93031ebfde67a4ae4a12bbe3ce</data>
