      <data key="d3">16.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Court uses Section 1516 to decide if there are legitimate grounds for divorce."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Court uses the grounds outlined in Section 1516 to determine the validity of a divorce claim."</data>
