      <data key="d3">9.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"The Seller delivers property to The Buyer under the contract terms, and both have specific duties and liabilities depending on the transaction conditions."</data>
      <data key="d5">"property transfer, contractual obligations"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-9ca3fcb51a635c23cbd4974dd21e277f</data>
    </edge>
