    <edge source="&quot;DEBTOR&quot;" target="&quot;COURT&quot;">
      <data key="d3">16.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"A Debtor may interact with the Court when disputes regarding the Obligation or its performance arise."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Court can annul acts by the Debtor that prejudice the Creditor, highlighting its protective role over creditor interests."</data>
      <data key="d5">"legal disputes, court orders"&lt;SEP&gt;"legal oversight, protection"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-6cd9b0e3cf4adfb36e41fca038140314&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac44eff8208c6427b97025d89925979e</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;DEBTOR&quot;" target="&quot;CREDITOR&quot;">
      <data key="d3">88.0</data>
      <data key="d4">"A creditor is owed a financial or contractual obligation by the debtor."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Creditor may exercise claims on behalf of the Debtor and is affected by the acts of the Debtor regarding their obligations and property security."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Debtor is obligated to perform certain actions or make payments to the Creditor."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Debtor owes a financial obligation to the Creditor, requiring performance or payment."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Debtor owes obligations or debts to the Creditor, and various legal proceedings and time-related conditions affect their interactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The creditor is owed obligations by the debtor, establishing a financial and legal relationship governed by the terms of a contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The debtor owes an obligation to the creditor that must be fulfilled, else the creditor can demand performance from the surety."&lt;SEP&gt;"The debtor owes an obligation to the creditor, who has the right to demand performance of the debt."&lt;SEP&gt;"The debtor owes obligations to creditors, who may enforce preferential rights to recover debts before others."&lt;SEP&gt;"The debtor owes obligations to the creditor and must perform them in due time, or else face consequences like default penalties and compensation claims."</data>
      <data key="d5">"debt obligation, financial rights"&lt;SEP&gt;"debt, legal rights"&lt;SEP&gt;"financial obligation, debts"&lt;SEP&gt;"financial obligation, legal conditions"&lt;SEP&gt;"financial obligation, legal duty"&lt;SEP&gt;"financial obligation, legal responsibility"&lt;SEP&gt;"financial obligation, legal rights"&lt;SEP&gt;"financial obligation, lender-borrower relationship"&lt;SEP&gt;"financial obligation, priority"&lt;SEP&gt;"obligation fulfillment, legal requirements"</data>
      <data key="d6">chunk-c35036965b446b68b1f64bc55f989965&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b194bfa1a18d3dffd302b027ba18352&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac44eff8208c6427b97025d89925979e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f23a6639e72b69e61fefaaa9a0d77c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5806a4ac5edf0880beed390e35f10ef7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-23efb3388014eb72630dbca0d161e5c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a51405b734dd6683f138a8765370d40b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6cd9b0e3cf4adfb36e41fca038140314&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7fb2f4e3c8f089ed58aad2cf781f6f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bac2de5ec87beec114bb4549e917cb4e</data>
    </edge>
